item.title: Link Roundup
item.description: The incredible philosophy of Ange Postecoglou Swift.org The Swift homepage got a facelift with more tutorials Blocking a Floating Tremolo on a Guitar BSD Now podcast - I’m really enjoying this podcast RunBSD.info - who uses BSD and why? The History of BSD Jails - I’m always amazed at how little work BSD Jails are and how much work Docker is LawrenceTV - more people need to love Lawrence as much as I do
